text: Kayrat Biekenov (born 25 May 1972) is a Kazakhstani ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Kazakhstan Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
